# Performance

## Known issues (fix when touching related code)
- Tesseract.js eager-loaded (~1–2 MB) — lazy-load on Care tab open only
- `initParticles()` runs while `.ambient` is hidden — remove or gate
- Full `render()` rebuilds all tabs — prefer partial render when safe
- 60s `loadData` poll — compare JSON hash before `render()`
- Three Google Font families — use `font-display: swap`

## Rules
1. Don't add new `requestAnimationFrame` loops without gating
2. Don't add new CDN scripts without lazy loading
3. Keep `index.html` diff minimal — currently ~98 KB
4. Cache-bust fetches: always `?v=` or `?t=` timestamp on JSON

## Mobile targets
- First meaningful paint: show skeleton within 100ms
- Interactive after `loadData()` + first `render()`
- Test slow 3G throttling mentally for every UI change

## Offline
- Pending bills → `localStorage` key `hospitalBillsLocal`
- `flushPendingToCloud()` on load when token present
- Don't break merge logic on silent refresh

## Measure impact in self-review
Score Performance /10. Below 8 → explain in session report.
